  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 200C.",
    "Toss the butternut cubes with olive oil, salt, pepper, smoked paprika, and sage.",
    "Spread the mixture in a cazuela and roast until caramelized, about 20 minutes.",
    "Whisk together eggs, cream, melted olive oil, minced garlic, salt, pepper, and smoked paprika until smooth.",
    "Stir in shredded mozzarella and crumbled feta.",
    "Remove the squash from the oven and arrange the smoked salmon on top.",
    "Pour the egg mixture evenly over the salmon and squash.",
    "Bake the quiche until set and the top is golden, about 15 minutes.",
    "Let the quiche cool for 5 minutes before slicing.",
    "Serve warm and optionally garnish with fresh sage leaves."
